					is utilized as <span class="redtext italicstext">v</span>HMML's front-end framework</li>
				<li><span class="redtext italicstext">v</span>HMML relies on <a href="https://www.elastic.co/products/elasticsearch" target="_blank">Elasticsearch</a> for indexing metadata and providing search results</li>
				<li><a href="https://w3id.org/" target="_blank">w3id</a> provides vHMML's permanent links implementation</li>
				<li>Special thanks to Jim Gramke and Josh Trutwin from <abbr
					title="College of St. Benedict/Saint John's University">CSB/SJU</abbr>
					IT Services for the server configuration, security and maintenance
				</li>
				
			</ul>
